places.perex: Le pont de la Margineda est le plus grand pont médiéval de la principauté d'Andorre.

places.name: Church of St. Coloma
places.perex: Andorra's oldest church and a marvellous historical gem. Beautifully decorated with Romanesque murals and the Baroque altar.

places.name: Parc Central, Andorra la Vella
places.perex: Parc Central is a park in Andorra la Vella, Andorra. It was designed by the architect Daniel Gelabert Fontova.

places.name: Church of St. Stephen
places.perex: A well-preserved Romanesque church from the 11th century. The stained windows and paintings depicting the Apocalypse are worth a look.

places.name: Town Square
places.perex: A popular assembling place for the people. Other than that, the views of the surrounding mountains are simply breath-taking from here.

places.name: Vallée du Madriu-Perafita-Claror
places.perex: La vallée du Madriu-Perafita-Claror est une vallée glaciaire pyrénéenne située au sud-est de la principauté d'Andorre.

places.name: Église Sant Romà de Les Bons
places.perex: L'église Sant Romà de Les Bons est une église romane situé dans le village de Les Bons, en Andorre.

places.name: Caldea
places.perex: Caldea est un centre thermoludique proposant principalement des activités de balnéothérapie.

places.name: La noblesse du temps. Salvador Dalí

places.perex: Notre Dame de Meritxell est une statue romane catholique d'Andorre représentant une apparition de la Vierge Marie.

places.name: Chapelle Sant Marc et Santa Maria d'Encamp
places.perex: La chapelle Sant Marc et Santa Maria est une église romane située à Encamp en Andorre.

places.name: Grandvalira Ski Resort

places.name: Valls del Nord Ski Resort

places.name: Naturlandia
places.perex: Be it winter or summer, this park makes for a wonderful day out. Tons of activities to choose from.

places.name: Monoprix

places.name: Perfume Museum

places.name: Church of Sant Miquel de Prats

places.name: Museum of Electricity, Encamp
places.perex: Explore the history of electricity production in Andorra. Take part in the fun experiments which will entertain both children and adults!

places.name: Casa Cristo Ethnographic Museum
places.perex: Casa Cristo is a house located in Encamp, Andorra. It is a heritage property registered in the Cultural Heritage of Andorra.

places.name: Pic de Coma Pedrosa
places.perex: Le pic de Coma Pedrosa est la montagne des Pyrénées la plus haute d'Andorre, culminant à 2 942 mètres.

places.name: Restaurant Grill La Sangria

places.name: Restaurant Manacor
places.perex: Taste delicious traditional dishes or something from charcoal grills. They offer daily menu and service in five different languages.

places.name: National Museum of Automobiles
places.perex: An outstanding collection of vehicles - from the oldest steam engine to the newest cars. A must-see for automobile fans.

places.perex: The mediaeval complex consists of Church of Sant Romà, a former defence tower and two watch towers. It overlooks the town of Encamp.

places.name: Golf Soldeu
places.perex: Since it is located at an altitude of 2,250 metres, you need to get there by a cable car. This exclusive 9-hole course will amaze you!

places.name: Tobacco Museum
places.perex: A well-laid out and informative museum with interactive exhibits. Learn about the craft that was once essential to Andorra.

places.name: Comapedrosa Communal Natural Park
places.perex: Set in the mountains, this park provides wonderful hiking opportunities.

places.name: Parc naturel de Sorteny
places.perex: Le parc naturel de Sorteny est le premier espace naturel protégé existant en Andorre. Il occupe une superficie de 1 080 ha.

places.perex: Le Pic de la Portelleta ou Tossa Plana de Lles est un sommet d'Andorre, situé dans la paroisse d'Escaldes-Engordany culminant à une…

places.name: Restaurant L'Abarset
places.perex: The conveniently located restaurant serves traditional meals. When it's sunny, you can enjoy your lunch outside on the terrace.

Restaurant Refugi del Llac de Pessons
Pont de Sant Antoni de la Grella
places.perex: Le pont de Sant Antoni de la Grella est un pont médiéval de la principauté d'Andorre, restauré au XXe siècle.

places.name: Estany de Les Truites
places.perex: L'Estany de les Truites est un lac d'Andorre situé dans la paroisse de La Massana.

places.name: Port de Siguer
places.perex: Le port de Siguer est un col de haute montagne de la chaîne pyrénéenne, situé sur la frontière entre Andorre et la France, sur le…

places.name: Santa Creu de Canillo
places.perex: Església de la Santa Creu de Canillo is a small church located in Canillo, Andorra.

places.name: Wellness Mountain Spa
places.perex: Pamper yourself with various massages and body treatments after a long day. You can enjoy them individually, in couples or in groups.

places.name: Ice Palace of Andorra
places.perex: Go ice karting, skating, or swimming. You can easily spend a day here with your friends or your family.

places.name: Family Park Canillo
places.perex: This entertaining park offers numerous activities for families. Go canoeing or horseback riding and enjoy the natural surroundings!

places.name: Incles Valley
places.perex: A breath-taking canyon. The nature here is wonderful and offers many sport opportunities - be it winter or summer.

places.name: Ahotels Mountain Spa
places.perex: Located at an altitude of 1,850 m, this spa offers a unique experience. Try indoor lagoon, contrast showers, sauna, hot tubs, and many more!

places.name: Motorcycle Museum, Canillo
places.perex: All fans of motorcycles will be excited by the exhibition of numerous machines. Explore their development over time.

places.name: La Vall del Riu Hiking Route
places.perex: This hiking trail goes through the forests and leads you to the refuge on a high plateau. Admire the huge variety of flowers around the path.

places.name: Escaldes-Engordany Arts Centre
places.perex: A cultural centre with two permanent exhibits. Do not miss the sculptures of the famous artist Josep Viladomat and the Romanesque miniatures…

places.name: Restaurant Cala Bassa Costa Rodona
places.perex: This place offers Mediterranean dishes. Eat on the terrace so that you can enjoy the views.

places.name: Postal Museum
places.perex: A wonderful museum that explains both the history of the postal system and has a huge collection of stamps on display.

places.name: Church of Sant Martí de la Cortinada
places.perex: Located in a picturesque town, this church is worth a visit for its Romanesque architecture and superb interior decoration.

places.name: Cross of the 7 Arms
places.perex: This ancient Gothic cross has only six arms instead of seven. It serves as a reminder of a tragic legend.

places.name: KSB Kamikaze Surf Bar
places.perex: The restaurant with magnificent views of the slopes serves steaks in all possible sizes! Excellent parties are also held here.

places.name: The Areny-Plandolit House Museum
places.perex: A beautiful 17th century house devoted to Andorra's noble family. See the luxurious furnishing and breathe in the atmosphere of the old…

places.name: The Racons Iron Way
places.perex: Take this 400 metres long and 210 metres high climb on the rock wall. Be careful, it is very demanding and there are no escape routes.
